planHighlights:
Checking Symphonix Value Inf.
Coverage for most commonly used prescription drugs.
The drug list includes most generic drugs and many commonly used brand name drugs covered by Medicare Part D.
You pay no more than 58% of the total cost for generic drugs or 45% of the total cost for brand name drugs, for any drug tier during the coverage gap.
$0 co-pay for a 90-day supply of Tier 1 and Tier 2 medications with home delivery from OptumRx.
